snippet.title: DuelingGun - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy the game at: https://gamedevchallenges.itch.io/dueling-gun

You are a gunslinger fighting rows of enemies in tense, both thinking and twitch reflex duels trough a number of stages from the wild west to outer space. Inspired by Spaghetti western movies themes and feels.

Follow the updates in:
Tumblr: https://gamedev-challenges.tumblr.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GamedevChallen1
